 />\n完"},{"pid":"1d114a153a56f9c3f5ee686cd025fdc2c8bd8264","tid":488923,"uid":60605,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T03:19:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>較鬧鐘又係好煩，iOS 要tap 多好多下<br />\n<br />\n改鬧鐘時間要上下掃好慢，stock android 較時間 tap 兩下就較好 (唔識形容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n同埋 android 較好左會顯示仲有幾耐會響，用黎double check 有冇較錯，iOS 就無呢個功能</blockquote><br />\nAndroid 可以喺未響之前熄咗佢，例如你校咗七點半響，但係你七點四已經醒咗，就可以熄咗唔駛等到七點半時佢響先熄"},{"pid":"33ba3aaae8655902bd59b2995924078f1975d4af","tid":488923,"uid":27146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T03:31:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>較鬧鐘又係好煩，iOS 要tap 多好多下<br />\n<br />\n改鬧鐘時間要上下掃好慢，stock android 較時間 tap 兩下就較好 (唔識形容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n同埋 android 較好左會顯示仲有幾耐會響，用黎double check 有冇較錯，iOS 就無呢個功能</blockquote><br />\nAndroid 可以喺未響之前熄咗佢，例如你校咗七點半響，但係你七點四已經醒咗，就可以熄咗唔駛等到七點半時佢響先熄</blockquote><br />\n叫siri熄左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"187416806d66e504117bad68e09cb543fc51ccba","tid":488923,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T03:35:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>習慣下食屎既感覺</blockquote><br />\nAndroid每次爆出嚟啲bug對你嚟講似啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef2d8d738e60e57978582b99ef15bf805e08fa6a","tid":488923,"uid":1886,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T03:39:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>就快轉ios<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但琴日見用ios嘅呀哥將youtube download嘅歌入落iphone到要搞好多野 又話要用itools itunes放相 冇得直接插usb放歌落去 但係又唔想再用an機<br />\n求指教andriod轉ios嘅人要改變嘅習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有錢買電話時，有錢買歌聽</blockquote><br />\n佢係download d marvel trailer 嘅音樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>